---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
    title="Hizmetlerimiz | Tente, Branda ve Çadır Sistemleri Çözümleri"
    description="Amir Branda olarak, çadır ve tente sistemlerinin kurulumu, kumaş değişimi, tamiri ve özel proje tasarımları için profesyonel destek sağlıyoruz."
    ogTitle="Hizmetlerimiz | Amir Branda"
    ogImage="https://branda.ist/style/brand/img/hizmetler-1.webp"
    headerTitle="Sizin İçin Neler Yapabiliriz?"
    headerTitleTag="h1"
    headerBgImage="/style/brand/img/kategori-arkasi-pp.webp"
    hideSidebar={true}
>
    <article class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-8">
        <!-- Intro Section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight"
                id="page"
            >
                Profesyonel Branda, Çadır ve Tente Hizmetleri
            </h2>
            <p
                class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm"
            >
                İstanbul'un lider <strong class="text-gray-900"
                    >branda ve tente imalatçısı</strong
                > olarak;
                <a
                    href="/branda-tente-imalati"
                    class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline"
                    title="branda tente imalatı">branda tente imalatı</a
                >, montajı ve satış sonrası
                <a
                    href="/tente-tamiri-bakimi"
                    class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline"
                    title="tente tamiri servis">tente tamiri servis</a
                > hizmetlerinde uzun ömürlü ve garantili çözümler sunuyoruz. Mafsallı
                tente, pergole tente, şeffaf branda uygulamaları ve endüstriyel depo
                çadırı sistemlerinden, küçük ölçekli balkon korumalarına kadar tüm
                ihtiyaçlarınız için uzman ekibimizle projelerinizi hayata geçiriyoruz.
                İhtiyacınıza özel, dayanıklı ve şık alan kapama sistemlerini avantajlı
                fiyat garantisiyle işleten güvenilir adresiniz.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Services Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
            <!-- Service 1: Imalat -->
            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col md:flex-row overflow-hidden"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-full md:w-5/12 relative overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center p-6 bg-gray-50 lg:border-r border-gray-100"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/style/brand/img/hizmetler-1.webp"
                        alt="Sakarya Tente ve Branda İmalatı"
                        class="w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-2xl transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-sm"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center flex-grow bg-white z-10"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-industry text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                    >
                        İmalat ve Kurulum
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Hangar çadırlarından otomatik pergolara kadar her alanda
                        projenize en uygun sistemi atölyemizde üretiyor ve uzman
                        montaj ekibimizle hızlıca adresinizde çalışır teslim
                        (anahtar teslim) kuruyoruz.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/iletisim"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold mt-auto hover:text-blue-700 transition"
                    >
                        Bilgi Alın <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 2: Tamir -->
            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col md:flex-row overflow-hidden"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-full md:w-5/12 relative overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center p-6 bg-gray-50 lg:border-r border-gray-100"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/style/brand/img/hizmetler-2.webp"
                        alt="Eskişehir Tente Tamiri ve Bakımı"
                        class="w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-2xl transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-sm"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center flex-grow bg-white z-10"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-green-50 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-wrench text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Tamir ve Bakım Servisi
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Zamanla arızalanan tente motorları, kırılan mafsal
                        kolları, sıkışan mekanizmalar veya yırtılan kumaşlar
                        için 7/24 randevu sistemimizle teknik destek ve hasar
                        tespit bakım onarım servisi sunuyoruz.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/tente-tamiri-bakimi"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-green-600 font-bold mt-auto hover:text-green-700 transition"
                    >
                        Servis Çağırın <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 3: Kumaş Yenileme -->
            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col md:flex-row overflow-hidden flex-row-reverse"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-full md:w-5/12 relative overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center p-6 bg-gray-50 lg:border-l border-gray-100"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/style/brand/img/hizmetler-3.webp"
                        alt="Balıkesir Branda ve Kumaş Yenileme"
                        class="w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-2xl transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-sm"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center flex-grow bg-white z-10"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-orange-50 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-fill-drip text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Kumaş & Branda Yenileme
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Güneşten solmuş veya eskimiş kumaşlarınızı söküyor,
                        iskeletiniz sağlamsa sadece kumaş değişimi yaparak
                        yepyeni ithal (Dikson, Sauleda) akrilik veya blackout
                        branda ile değiştiriyoruz.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/iletisim"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-orange-500 font-bold mt-auto hover:text-orange-600 transition"
                    >
                        Değişim Talebi <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 4: Özel Projeler -->
            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col md:flex-row overflow-hidden flex-row-reverse"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-full md:w-5/12 relative overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center p-6 bg-gray-50 lg:border-l border-gray-100"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/style/brand/img/hizmetler-4.webp"
                        alt="Muğla Mimari Branda ve Özel Projeler"
                        class="w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-2xl transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-sm"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center flex-grow bg-white z-10"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-compass-drafting text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Mimari & Özel Projelendirme
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Restoran, otel, fabrika ve büyük müstakil projelerinizde
                        yerinizde ücretsiz keşif sağlıyor; alanınıza en uygun
                        mimari tasarımı yapıp sadece mekana özel kalıplarla
                        endüstriyel çözümler sunuyoruz.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/iletisim"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-purple-600 font-bold mt-auto hover:text-purple-700 transition"
                    >
                        Keşif İsteyin <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action Banner -->
        <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-2xl bg-slate-900 p-10 md:p-16 text-center"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-primary/20 to-slate-800"
            >
            </div>

            <!-- decorative blur -->
            <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-20 -mr-20 w-64 h-64 bg-primary rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-30"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-20 -ml-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-400 rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-20"
            >
            </div>

            <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h4
                    class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight"
                >
                    İhtiyacınız Olan Hizmeti Hemen Planlayalım
                </h4>
                <p
                    class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Branda üretim, kumaş yenileme veya motor montajı gibi
                    işlemlerinizde alanında uzman ekibimiz bir telefon
                    uzağınızda ücretsiz keşif onayı için bekliyor.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                    <a
                        href="/iletisim"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-primary text-white font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(76,166,229,0.4)] hover:bg-blue-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_8px_25px_rgba(76,166,229,0.6)] transition-all duration-300"
                    >
                        Bizimle İletişime Geçin <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane ml-3"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="https://wa.me/905386044851"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-green-500 text-white font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(34,197,94,0.4)] hover:bg-green-400 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_8px_25px_rgba(34,197,94,0.6)] transition-all duration-300"
                    >
                        WhatsApp'tan Yazın <i
                            class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp ml-3 text-xl"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</PageLayout>
